&none  &kp TAB    &kp EQUAL      &kp LEFT_BRACE  &kp LEFT_BRACKET  &kp DOUBLE_QUOTES    &kp SINGLE_QUOTE  &kp RIGHT_BRACKET  &kp RIGHT_BRACE  &kp PLUS          &kp CARET  &none
